'''Ronald James McLean''' {{post-nominals|country=NZL|MBE}} (22 January 1914&ndash;26 May 1980) was a New Zealand farmer, aviator, community leader and environmental campaigner. He was born in [[Wyndham, New Zealand|Wyndham]], [[Southland Region|Southland]], [[New Zealand]] on 22 January 1914.<ref name="DNZB McLean">{{DNZB|title=Ronald James McLean|first= Alan F.|last= Mark|id=5m23|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

